In case you don't know this legend....Let me introduce you to Lisa Johnson, Rock Photographer, she's been a superstar in the music business for 30+ years. 
You've seen her photos and maybe didn't even realize they have all been shot by Lisa (who is also my longtime friend)
💫Starting Day 1 of the Vans Warped Tour....Lisa's instincts told her that was the beginning of a cultural revolution and it needed to be documented....She spent 25 years on the tour as the official photographer. 
Lisa has shot all our favorite bands from Nirvana to RATM and the Smashing Pumpkins to Rise Against, NOFX, A7X and a million more. She also took the very first photos for Linkin Park once they were signed. 
You know the pic of Bradley Nowell with Lou and Jacob on the couch?  Lisa shot that.  Some of her work is featured in the new Punk Rock Museum in Vegas. 
She's also taken pictures of yours truly. 
The music business under the rock umbrella can be very tough, Lisa continues to shine because of her crazy talent, but also, she's a wonderful and strong human
🖤It was great seeing you Saturday night at Sad Summer Fest🖤
.
.
#lisajohnsonrockphotographer #smashingpumpkins #rageagainstthemachine  #warpedtour #nirvana #kurtcobain #davegrohl #avengedsevenfold #riseagainst
